title: Energ Bites (150gm)
description: A delicious fusion of all things yummy and nutritious. Each mouthful is intended to increase your energy levels, keep you satisfied, yet leave you wanting for more.
details:
Best part:
  • - Dairy Free
  • - Preservative Free
  • - No added Sugar
  • - No added Oil

Who can consume: Absolutely anyone!

Our energy bites are perfect for :
  • - Pre or post workout snack
  • - Busy professionals
  • - Growing children
  • - Senior citizens
  • - Overworked moms & housewives

Caution: Contains nuts and seeds; diabetic patients should restrict consumption to one bite per day or consult the doctor before consuming
Storage Instructions: Keep the box in the refrigerator for at least two hours after you receive it. The energy bites should generally be kept in the refrigerator because they contain natural oil that will discharge if not (especially in humid areas/climates).
